title: Blind Karaoke Is Back! + Is Amy Being Scammed? + Eddie Confronts A Road Rage Driver
itunes:title: Blind Karaoke Is Back! + Is Amy Being Scammed? + Eddie Confronts A Road Rage Driver
description:
Bobby has Amy, Eddie and Lunchbox compete in a karaoke competition where they don’t get to see the lyrics while singing the song. Amy wants to know if she’s being scammed by a cat breeder who she paid money to for a cat…but never got it! We scold Eddie for a road rage incident that he took too far.
